{
  "texts": [
    "\"-ChatGPT 3.5As you can see, this model is capable of creating grammatically correct sentences, related to a specified topic, in a very simple and accessible manner: I can converse with it as if I was speaking to a person.",
    "When playing around with it, you will quickly realise that it is an incredibly powerful tool that can answer in virtually any language (programming languages included) and about almost every topic.",
    "At some point, you may find yourself asking \"is there anything it can't do?\".",
    "The answer (luckily) is yes, and the reason behind it requires a look under the hood.LLMs and most of the models on which GenAI operates are probabilistic models.",
    "This means that it decides which word comes next based on probability [32]."
  ]
}